<subSubSection lastPageId="32" lastPageNumber="325" pageId="31" pageNumber="324" type="description">
<paragraph blockId="31.[151,1436,1973,2034]" lastBlockId="32.[151,1436,151,285]" lastPageId="32" lastPageNumber="325" pageId="31" pageNumber="324">
This species was reported only during the exploratory surveys on the 
<number box="[987,1048,2010,2034]" pageId="31" pageNumber="324" value="1980.0">1980</number>
s. Length data from 
<quantity box="[1272,1436,2010,2034]" metricMagnitude="0" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.56" metricValueMax="3.22" metricValueMin="1.9" pageId="31" pageNumber="324" unit="cm" value="256.0" valueMax="322.0" valueMin="190.0">190 to 322 cm</quantity>
TL, but the number of individuals were not reported. Habitat and Distribution: pelagic-oceanic species preferring temperatures from 
<number box="[366,394,188,212]" pageId="32" pageNumber="325" value="18.0">18</number>
°C to 
<number box="[463,493,188,212]" pageId="32" pageNumber="325" value="22.0">22</number>
°C at depths ranging between 
<quantity box="[834,937,188,212]" metricMagnitude="2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="4.0" metricValueMax="8.0" metricValueMin="0.0" pageId="32" pageNumber="325" unit="m" value="400.0" valueMax="800.0" valueMin="0.0">0–800 m</quantity>
, usually 
<quantity box="[1039,1142,188,213]" metricMagnitude="2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.75" metricValueMax="5.5" metricValueMin="0.0" pageId="32" pageNumber="325" unit="m" value="275.0" valueMax="550.0" valueMin="0.0">
0– 
<specimenCount box="[1067,1142,188,213]" pageId="32" pageNumber="325" type="generic">550 m</specimenCount>
</quantity>
. Worldwide distributed in the Atlantic, Pacific, and Indian oceans in tropical, temperate, and sometimes cold waters. Vulnerability: LC (
<collectionCode box="[159,233,260,284]" pageId="32" pageNumber="325">IUCN</collectionCode>
), HHV (FishBase).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
